<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbcdffde5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s4772"><num value="4772">§ 4772.</num><heading> Effective date of grant provisions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Grant provisions of this chapter shall become effective one hundred and eighty days following <date date="1971-01-05">January 5, 1971</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbcdffde6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/648/tV/s513">Pub. L. 91–648, title V, § 513</ref>, <date date="1971-01-05">Jan. 5, 1971</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1929">84 Stat. 1929</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbcdffde7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbcdffde8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idbcdffde9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in text, means the provisions of subchapters I, II, III, and IV of this chapter. See <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s4761">section 4761 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
